  accentWord="Plumbing"
  subhead={`You cannot answer the phone when the blow torch is heating a 22mm copper joint, when you are crawling through floor joists running first-fix pipework, or when your arms are inside a bathroom stud wall connecting waste to the soil stack. Your AI receptionist captures every call, every message, and every tender — from main contractors commissioning thirty-two-plot estate plumbing to homeowners needing a leaking stopcock replaced. From £${pricing.tiers.core.price}/month.`}
